@node "History" "History of RunBar"


   @{fg highlight}Version 0.9@{fg text}

       First program version.

   @{fg highlight}Version 1.0@{fg text}

       Fixed bug associated with Drawers rename,remove and add.

   @{fg highlight}Version 1.1@{fg text}

       Commodity support added.Now you can Enable,Disable program or
       Quit from program using Exchange program.

       HotKey added (Default F1).When you press hotkey RunBar window
       will POPUP.

       GFX improvement.

   @{fg highlight}Version 1.2@{fg text}

       Removed little popup problem.

       Changed Find and Clock GFX.

       Added Find and Clock programs coded by me.

   @{fg highlight}Version 1.3@{fg text}

       Added popup delay.

       Now you can change spacing between items.

       Added Prefs program.

   @{fg highlight}Version 2.0@{fg text}

       Bildin Exchange program.Now you can control other programs from
       RunBar!!!!!

       Now if you change Prefs, it take effect immediately.

       Added error requesters.Now you can know why program won't run.

       When you press HotKey window popup under mouse pointer.

       Middle mouse button support as HotKey.(Only for Standart Amiga
       mouse!!!!!)

   @{fg highlight}Version 2.1@{fg text}

       Fixed menu layout bug.

       Improved screen management.

   @{fg highlight}Version 2.2@{fg text}

       Bug fixed. If you skip all commodities and try to popup RunBar
       program crash.

       Fixed few little bugs.

   @{fg highlight}Version 2.3@{fg text}

       New feature.In this version you can exclude files from Prefs menu.

       New feature.Configurable Utilities menu.

   @{fg highlight}Version 2.4@{fg text}

       Configurable images.

       ASL requester in Command window.

       Fixed Command execute bug.

       Changed clock font.

       Prefs caching.

       Add,Remove,NewDrawer,Command windows now font sensitive.

       New menus access method.

   @{fg highlight}Version 3.0@{fg text}

       Full font and images sensetive.

       Anim on/off.

       Prefs state remember.

       Show prefs only with icons.(Optional)

       100% standard code.(No hacks and etc.)

       Windows control.(No only commodities)

       Keyboard control.

       Items Add and Edit improvement.
       
   @{fg highlight}Version 3.1@{fg text}
   
       New ULTIMATE program control Port. (SDK included).

       Turn off - safe computer turn off (Unmount all devices).
   
       Different window borders.

       Recessed items selection.

       Removed keyboard control bug.

       Quit,Turn off,Reboot,Remove requesters.
@endnode

@node "Requirements" "System Requirements"


 To run RunBar you need to have some hardware and software:


   @{fg highlight}*@{fg text} OS 3.0+ (V39+)

   @{fg highlight}*@{fg text} MagicWB colors.

   @{fg highlight}*@{fg text} wbstart.library
     (c) 1991-1996 Stefan Becker. (Included into archive)
     Also you can find archive on Aminet util/libs/WBStart2_2.lha.

   @{fg highlight}*@{fg text} XHelvetica.font (Comes with MagicWB).
     Please use only standart XHelvetica fonts!!!!!

   @{fg highlight}*@{fg text} MUI (c) Stefan Stuntz. (Only for Find and Prefs programs).
@endnode

@node "Introduction" "Introduction"

 @{fg highlight}Introduction@{fg text}

  This program is replacement for ToolManager. Using this you can
  easy run your programs,tools,prefs,ARexx scripts and etc...

  You'll have fast access to programs,just few mouse click!!!!!!
@endnode

