@node "Window" "Window"


  POPUP RunBar window:

    Move mouse pointer to bottom of workbench screen,RunBar window
    appears there.Press Start button to POPUP main window.

    Also you can popup window with Hotkey (default is F1.) or
    with middle mouse button ,if this function enabled.

    Select menu items by moving mouse poiner over it.

    If you want open second menus move mouse pointer to right of current
    menu or press left mouse button ,or wait time delay if you use
    Time Delay access method.

  ShutDown:

      Quit - Exit.

      Reboot - reboot computer.
      
      Turn Off - Unmount all volumes and you can safe turn off computer.

  Command:

    Execute command string.

  Utilities:

    Now seven utilities are supported.

      Clock - clock.

      Find - file finder. (At this time I have no time to write my own
                           find utility.Rename any find utility to "Find"
                           and copy it to SYS:Utilities directory.)

      Also you can add up to 5 your own Utilities.

  Prefs:

    This is directory SYS:Prefs mirror.You can start from here prefs
    programs.

  Programs:

    From this window you can start your programs.

    At first program run this window don't contain any item.
    To add item move mouse pointer right, and popup window with
    "Empty" item. Move mouse over this window, press right mouse
    button and keep it pressed, Select one of four options:

    Add Drawer:  Add drawer to current window.

    Rename: Rename current highlighted item or drawer.

    Remove: Remove current item or drawer:

    Add File: Add programs to current window.
              (New window will open. Drop program icon into this window
               and select program type.Then press OK button).

  Windows control:

    When RunBar popup you can see buttons with windows names.Press on this
    buttons if you want move this window to front and make it active.
@endnode

